freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Just seem to have more fatigue again-had it first 72hrs after vaccine then resolved. Today is 14days after 2nd dose, been quite tired again last maybe 3 days

Since 12/28/31 developed both itchy eyes. Left eye more irritated, slight droop outer corner left eyelid. Eye can feel heavy. Started getting little better today. I do have allergies but more during spring/fall-not now in winter in nj

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Feel normal then cold/often but no more cold sweats. I usually before vaccine get menopause hot flashes not like cold flash.
Slight dizzy, feeling stiff not muscle ache, ache across back of hands
Still get cold/alternate regular temp but no more cold sweats. Never had shaking/chills.
Still had hit/cold with cold sweats in am, mostly resolved by 2pm
